00:44:01,966 --> 00:44:04,866
♫ for a lifetime's sorrows and joys. ♫

666
00:44:05,500 --> 00:44:08,166
♫ Tens of thousands of miles is not enough, ♫

667
00:44:08,766 --> 00:44:11,666
♫ for the endless seas and rivers. ♫

